name: MSI Educative Slide Image Gen v2

parameters.jsCode:
// Prepare Gemini Input - Build complete EDUCATIVE slide image prompt
const inputData = $('Webhook - Educative Slide Gen').item.json;
const input = inputData.body || inputData;
// Logo base64 is now embedded directly in the previous node (no HTTP download needed)
const logoBase64 = $('Download MSI Logo').item.json.logo_base64 || '';

// Extract all slide content fields
const slideNumber = parseInt(input.slide_number) || 1;
const headline = input.headline || '';
const subtext = input.subtext || '';
const bodyText = input.body_text || '';
const topic = input.topic || 'Professional Development';

// NO SOURCE for educational content
let educationalContext = 'Educational Content';
try {
  if (input.visual_style) {
    const vs = typeof input.visual_style === 'string' ? JSON.parse(input.visual_style) : input.visual_style;
    educationalContext = vs.topic || 'Educational Content';
  }
} catch (e) {
  educationalContext = 'Educational Content';
}

const isBlueSlide = (slideNumber === 1 || slideNumber === 3 || slideNumber === 5);
const paginationNumber = slideNumber;

let fullPrompt = '';

if (slideNumber === 1) {
  fullPrompt = `Create a 4:5 Instagram carousel SLIDE 1 for MSI Technologies TIPS content.

LOGO (CRITICAL - WHITE VERSION):
- Place the attached MSI logo in TOP-LEFT corner
- Logo size: approximately 60-80 pixels height, proportional width
- INVERT the logo colors: every BLUE (#207CE5) pixel becomes WHITE (#FFFFFF) and every WHITE pixel becomes BLUE (#207CE5). This creates a WHITE version of the logo for the blue gradient background.
- Keep the EXACT same design, shape, proportions and details - ONLY swap the colors.
- The result should be a crisp WHITE logo visible against the blue gradient.

LAYOUT:
- ENTIRE SLIDE: Gradient background from MSI Blue #207CE5 to Dark Blue #004AAD
- NO PHOTO. Solid gradient background ONLY.
- MAIN VISUAL: A striking 3D ANIMATED-STYLE element that DIRECTLY REPRESENTS the topic "${topic}". The 3D element must be a RECOGNIZABLE OBJECT or SYMBOL related to the specific topic - for example:
  * AI topic  3D brain, neural network shape, robot head
  * Automation  3D mechanical arm, conveyor, workflow arrows
  * Cloud  3D floating data cubes, digital storage blocks
  * Data  3D charts, graph visualization, data stream
  * Security  3D shield, digital lock
  * Productivity  3D clock, calendar, dashboard
  * Business  3D building blocks, growth arrow
  Choose the most RELEVANT 3D object for "${topic}". NOT generic abstract shapes - make it TOPIC-SPECIFIC.
- Position creatively (top-right, bottom-left, or asymmetric)
- 3D ELEMENT COLORS: Use WHITE, CREAM #FFFDF1, or SILVER tones ONLY. NO blue, NO gold. The element must CONTRAST against the blue gradient.
- The 3D element should have glossy/metallic finish, subtle glow effects, and appear to float with depth

FORBIDDEN VISUAL ELEMENTS:
- NO servers or server racks
- NO cloud icons or cloud shapes
- NO network connection lines or node diagrams
- NO circuit boards or chip patterns
- NO binary code (0s and 1s)
- NO globe with connections
- NO gears or cogs
- NO illustrations or cartoons
- NO photographs or realistic images
- NO people

TYPOGRAPHY (MANDATORY):
- HEADINGS: Use ITC Avant Garde font (bold, geometric sans-serif)
- BODY/CONTENT: Use Quicksand font (rounded, friendly sans-serif)
- ALL text must have NORMAL proportions - NOT stretched, NOT condensed, NOT elongated

TEXT CONTENT:
- VERY LARGE bold title in ITC Avant Garde, color WHITE #FFFFFF: "${headline}" - Position text to COMPLEMENT the 3D element
- Below the headline, SMALLER text (HEADING 2) in Quicksand font, color CREAM #FFFDF1: "${subtext}" - This indicates the content type (e.g. Quick Tips, Good to Know, Smart Moves)
- Bottom-RIGHT corner (visible): "Swipe >>>" in Quicksand, color WHITE #FFFFFF

FORBIDDEN: Photos, people, stretched text, condensed fonts, illustrations, cartoons, generic stock imagery, blue 3D elements, gold elements.`;

} else if (slideNumber === 5) {
  fullPrompt = `Create a 4:5 Instagram carousel SLIDE 5 - Educational CTA for MSI Technologies.

LOGO (CRITICAL - WHITE VERSION):
- Place the attached MSI logo in TOP-LEFT corner
- Logo size: approximately 60-80 pixels height, proportional width
- INVERT the logo colors: every BLUE (#207CE5) pixel becomes WHITE (#FFFFFF) and every WHITE pixel becomes BLUE (#207CE5). This creates a WHITE version of the logo for the blue gradient background.
- Keep the EXACT same design, shape, proportions and details - ONLY swap the colors.
- The result should be a crisp WHITE logo visible against the blue gradient.

LAYOUT:
- ENTIRE SLIDE: Gradient background from MSI Blue #207CE5 to Dark Blue #004AAD
- NO photo - solid gradient only
- Content vertically centered

TYPOGRAPHY (MANDATORY):
- HEADINGS: Use ITC Avant Garde font (bold, geometric sans-serif)
- BODY/CONTENT: Use Quicksand font (rounded, friendly sans-serif)
- ALL text must have NORMAL proportions - NOT stretched, NOT condensed, NOT elongated

TEXT CONTENT (centered):
- HEADING 1 (VERY LARGE, bold, ITC Avant Garde), color WHITE #FFFFFF: "${headline}"
- HEADING 2 (Medium size, below heading 1, Quicksand), color CREAM #FFFDF1: "${subtext || "Let's Learn Together"}"

CONTACT INFO (bottom center, LARGE text in Quicksand, color WHITE #FFFFFF):
- Line 1: envelope icon then contact@msitechnologiesinc.com
- Line 2: globe icon then msitechnologiesinc.com

FORBIDDEN: News elements, stretched text, condensed fonts, @ symbols, pagination, modifying the logo.`;

} else if (slideNumber === 2 || slideNumber === 4) {
  fullPrompt = `Create a 4:5 Instagram carousel SLIDE ${slideNumber} for MSI Technologies EDUCATIONAL content.

LOGO (CRITICAL - DO NOT MODIFY):
- Place the attached MSI logo (blue version) EXACTLY as provided in TOP-LEFT corner, overlaying the photo
- Logo size: approximately 60-80 pixels height, proportional width
- DO NOT resize, redraw, recreate, or modify the logo in ANY way

CRITICAL LAYOUT (ABSOLUTE REQUIREMENT - NO EXCEPTIONS):
- *** THE PHOTO MUST TOUCH THE VERY TOP EDGE OF THE IMAGE. y=0, pixel row 0. ZERO gap. ZERO margin. ZERO padding. NO white bar. NO white strip. NO white space above the photo. ***
- The photograph MUST be FLUSH with the top border of the canvas - there must be NOTHING between the top edge and the photo.
- If there is even 1 pixel of white space above the photo, the image is WRONG.
- Top 55%: REALISTIC PHOTOGRAPH (edge-to-edge, touching all borders at top) related to "${headline}". ABSOLUTELY NO PEOPLE - show only objects, devices, tech tools, workspaces without humans.
- The photo must span the FULL WIDTH of the slide and start at the ABSOLUTE TOP.
- Apply subtle BLUE GRADIENT at bottom edge of photo blending into white.
- Bottom 45%: Clean WHITE background for text.

REALISTIC PHOTOGRAPHY REQUIREMENTS:
- Professional, high-quality realistic photo with TECHNOLOGY FOCUS
- Show modern TECH in action: laptops, tablets, software dashboards, digital tools, AI interfaces
- Clean, editorial photography feel
- Directly related to the TECHNOLOGY tip being discussed

FORBIDDEN:
- NO servers, NO cloud icons, NO circuit boards, NO binary code
- NO news/media elements, NO illustrations, NO infographics

TYPOGRAPHY (MANDATORY):
- HEADINGS: ITC Avant Garde (bold, geometric sans-serif)
- BODY: Quicksand (rounded, friendly sans-serif)
- Body text must be SHORT but DESCRIPTIVE (max 3 lines, includes insight + why it matters)

TEXT (on white section, left-aligned):
- Headline in ITC Avant Garde, color MSI BLUE #207CE5: "${headline}"
  If the headline has a number prefix (Tip #N, Way #N, Fact #N, etc.), display it prominently in BLUE #207CE5.
- Body text in Quicksand, color DARK GRAY #333333, SMALL font, max 3 lines: "${bodyText}"
- Bottom-right in Quicksand, color GRAY #999999: "${paginationNumber}/5"

TECH FOCUS: The photo MUST show TECHNOLOGY - devices, screens, software, digital tools, tech workspaces. Always convey a TECHNOLOGICAL context related to the tip.

NO Source field. DO NOT modify logo.

*** FINAL REMINDER: The photo MUST start at y=0 (the absolute top pixel of the canvas). There must be ZERO white space, ZERO gap, ZERO margin above the photo. The image must be FLUSH with the top edge. This is the #1 most important layout rule. ***`;

} else {
  fullPrompt = `Create a 4:5 Instagram carousel SLIDE ${slideNumber} for MSI Technologies EDUCATIONAL content.

LOGO (CRITICAL - DO NOT MODIFY):
- Place the attached MSI logo EXACTLY as provided in TOP-LEFT corner
- Logo size: approximately 60-80 pixels height, proportional width
- DO NOT resize, redraw, recreate, or modify the logo in ANY way

CRITICAL LAYOUT (ABSOLUTE REQUIREMENT - NO EXCEPTIONS):
- *** THE PHOTO MUST TOUCH THE VERY TOP EDGE OF THE IMAGE. y=0, pixel row 0. ZERO gap. ZERO margin. ZERO padding. NO white bar. NO white strip. NO white space above the photo. ***
- The photograph MUST be FLUSH with the top border of the canvas - there must be NOTHING between the top edge and the photo.
- If there is even 1 pixel of white space above the photo, the image is WRONG.
- Top 55%: REALISTIC PHOTOGRAPH (edge-to-edge, touching all borders at top) related to "${headline}". ABSOLUTELY NO PEOPLE - show only tech objects, devices, tools.
- The photo must span the FULL WIDTH of the slide and start at the ABSOLUTE TOP.
- Apply BLUE GRADIENT overlay at bottom of photo blending into blue section.
- Bottom 45%: Solid MSI Blue #207CE5

REALISTIC PHOTOGRAPHY REQUIREMENTS:
- Professional, high-quality realistic photo with TECHNOLOGY FOCUS
- Show TECH from a different angle: close-ups of devices, software UIs, digital tools in use
- Clean, editorial photography feel

FORBIDDEN:
- NO servers, NO cloud icons, NO circuit boards, NO binary code
- NO news/media elements, NO illustrations

TYPOGRAPHY (MANDATORY):
- HEADINGS: ITC Avant Garde (bold, geometric sans-serif)
- BODY: Quicksand (rounded, friendly sans-serif)
- Body text must be SHORT but DESCRIPTIVE (max 3 lines, includes insight + why it matters)

TEXT (on blue section, left-aligned):
- Headline in ITC Avant Garde, color WHITE #FFFFFF: "${headline}"
  If the headline has a number prefix (Tip #N, Way #N, Fact #N, etc.), display it prominently in WHITE #FFFFFF.
- Body text in Quicksand, color CREAM #FFFDF1, SMALL font, max 3 lines: "${bodyText}"
- Bottom-right in Quicksand, color CREAM #FFFDF1: "${paginationNumber}/5"

TECH FOCUS: The photo MUST show TECHNOLOGY - devices, screens, digital tools, tech environments. Always convey a TECHNOLOGICAL context.

NO Source field. ABSOLUTELY NO PEOPLE in the photo. REALISTIC PHOTOGRAPHY only.

*** FINAL REMINDER: The photo MUST start at y=0 (the absolute top pixel of the canvas). There must be ZERO white space, ZERO gap, ZERO margin above the photo. The image must be FLUSH with the top edge. This is the #1 most important layout rule. ***`;
}

return [{
  json: {
    image_prompt: fullPrompt,
    slide_id: input.slide_id,
    carousel_id: input.carousel_id,
    slide_number: slideNumber,
    headline: headline,
    subtext: subtext,
    body_text: bodyText,
    educational_context: educationalContext,
    topic: topic,
    is_blue_slide: isBlueSlide,
    logo_base64: logoBase64
  }
}];

parameters.query:
=UPDATE carousel_slides 
SET image_url = '{{ $json.data.url }}', 
    updated_at = NOW()
WHERE id = '{{ $('Extract Binary').item.json.slide_id }}'
RETURNING *
